Insider Activity


Individual




J. Brendan Herron



Mr. J. B. Herron, Jr. MBA, is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at Hannon Armstrong Sustainable Infrastructure Capital, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Calvert Hall College.
Mr. Herron was previously employed as a Principal by Aggregate Industries Management, Inc., a Principal by Ernst & Young LLP, Senior Vice President by Hannon Armstrong Capital LLC, and Vice President-Corporate Development & Strategy by CURRENT Group LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from Loyola University Maryland and an MBA from Loyola University Maryland.



